title: Star Tunez
overview: Star Tunez is a weekly music series that brings viewers the very latest news, gossip, releases and chart rundowns from around the world. It looks into the lives of the music industry's hottest artists and discovers what it's like to live your life on stage. From glamorous award ceremonies to show-stopping performances to how artists use social media, Star Tunez reveals the private moments of the music world's biggest stars as well as some quickly rising newcomers.
